PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADIAN AVIATION REGULATIONS (PART VII) by specifying that the exemption regarding the need for a pilot proficiency check or competency check only applies to the manoeuvre it was intended to allow, meaning only when the chief pilot is in command of a single-engined aeroplane WITH NO PASSENGERS ON BOARD.

precis:
Regulations Amending the CANADIAN AVIATION REGULATIONS (PART VII) by
specifying that the exemption regarding the need for a pilot proficiency
check or competency check only applies to the manoeuvre it was intended to
allow, meaning only when the chief pilot is in command of a single-engined
aeroplane WITH NO PASSENGERS ON BOARD.
